e opportunity to explain any mitigating circumstances by 8 July and has until 3 October to present a plan of management actions designed to reduce the ratio between total non-performing loans and total loans to 20 per cent by 2018.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the situation is not entirely without hope.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although many banks have struggled to offload their bad loans, Banco Popolare revealed last Thursday - one week after the UK's EU membership vote took place - that it had agreed a sale on \\\\\\\\u20ac53.8m worth of such debt.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": []}]}"